{"root":{"data":{"id":"di2c7je3vao0","created":1777130565863,"text":"游戏概念与机制设想"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2ck8uj1ow0","created":1777131561646,"text":"世界观与背景概念","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di2cf6favig0","created":1777131164551,"text":"角色艺术概念","layout_mind_offset":{"x":709.999971787136,"y":159.99999364217143},"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2cfcoclq00","created":1777131178159,"text":"玩家在非战斗状态是一个可爱角色形象, 但在战斗状态切换为一个酷的风格, 但整体保持美术风格统一, 类似于埼玉的那种反差感","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"di2chepwpq80","created":1777131339335,"text":"角色能力","expandState":"expand","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2c834w6bk0","created":1777130608842,"text":"连招系统","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2c8i7cdi80","created":1777130641642,"text":"将连击的每段设置为不同层级,每段动作美感和复杂程度提升, 但是能在每个层级内挑选一个动作, 达到随机衔接招式的目的","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di2cbn6tj200","created":1777130887587,"text":"当敌人无法反抗时的斩击动作, (比如眩晕):按住常规x 攻击键的同时摇动手柄摇杆或者鼠标, 驱动动画疯狂斩击敌人","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"di2chm9yp880","created":1777131355785,"text":"技能树","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2chqybkrk0","created":1777131365965,"text":"让玩家在初始状态就拥有全部技能的使用权力, 但是随着玩家的偏好(例如使用某种技能最多), 那些技能会逐渐变强, 类似于通过训练逐渐掌握技能一样","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"3D角色精力条系统","expandState":"expand","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"核心概念","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"精力值","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"精力条","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"实现方式","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"UI设计","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"精力条样式","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"数字显示","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"编程实现","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"变量定义","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"当前精力值","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"最大精力值","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"恢复速度","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"消耗量","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"函数定义","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"消耗精力","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"恢复精力","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"更新UI","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"影响因素","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"角色动作","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"跑步","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"攻击","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"施法","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"游戏机制","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"休息","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"道具","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"技能","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"优化与扩展","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"特效","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"动画","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"粒子效果","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"多样性","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"pp","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]}]},"template":"filetree","theme":"classic","version":"1.4.43"}